	<key>readme</key>
	<string>Three ChatGPT prompt modes powered by the local `codex` CLI (uses your ChatGPT subscription via the OpenAI Responses API — no API key required).

• `g  &lt;query&gt;`  Ephemeral one-shot answer in Alfred. Not saved.
• `gg &lt;query&gt;`  Persistent: opens chatgpt.com with your prompt and auto-submits.
• `gt &lt;query&gt;`  Generate a shell command and paste it into the frontmost terminal.

Requirements: `codex` (ChatGPT-CLI) and `jq` available on PATH (Homebrew default `/opt/homebrew/bin` is added automatically).
</string>
